1) Lua
- downlaod at http://www.lua.org
- tar zxf lua-5.*.tar.gz
- cd lua-5.*
make linux
make linux test
make linux install

2) Lua POSIX
- install luarocks https://luarocks.org/
- sudo luarocks install luaposix 33.4.0

3) WSAPI & Xavante
- sudo luarocks install wsapi-xavante

4) Lua XML-RPC
git clone https://github.com/timn/lua-xmlrpc
- modify makefile, then
sudo make install

5) Lua MD5
sudo luarocks install md5

6) Lua Signal
sudo luarocks install lua_signal
